data.description: Your Perfect Play Place Awaits! Charming Curb Appeal w/Gated Front Courtyard & Freshly Painted Exterior. Kitchen Upgraded w/Stylish Slab Granite Counters, Granite Sink, New Faucet, Custom Backsplash, White Cabinets, Pendant Lighting & R/O. Park Like Backyard Features Large Extended Covered Patio & Blt In BBQ. 4 Ft Ext'd Garage Has Plenty Of Cabinets, Sink, Service Door & Newer Water Heater.
